{
  "stem": "8784.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We knew that he went, and we somehow-- either he told somebody and somebody told somebody else, and before you know the whole camp knew it, that Schindler was called into headquarters to answer charges.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were standing by the windows, doors, awaiting Schindler, our protector.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's the only one that can protect us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And lo and behold, sometimes late in the day, Oskar Schindler arrives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And if I understood it, when he loaded up-- when he went there, he went there with a load of whiskey and chocolates and everything in his car that he took off to the headquarters.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But when he came back, he was drunk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember seeing him in drunken state, getting out of that car of his and calling for the engineer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And if I recall it correctly, the engineer's name-- a German engineer, not a-- not a Polish or a Jewish inmate, but a German engineer by the name of-- of [?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Sherbourne ?] or [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Shelbourne ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He called him out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in German, we could-- now, I couldn't hear the details or anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But he was pointing out to him and yelling that over here on this side, we will have to build a-- a tall-- at that time, I understood it somehow to be 30-foot tall fence, solid so that people couldn't see to the inside of the camp.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, those-- those things I remember by myself seeing and happening in a clear mind already because this was towards the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we possibly even began to think, which did not happen in-- up to this point, really.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
